<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīkākatirājyapravarddha
<lb n="2" break="no"/>mānavijayurāja śakavarṣaṁbulu 1162
<lb n="3"/>nēṁṭi Uttarāyaṇasaṁkrāṁttinimittamuna <unclear>mi</unclear>
<lb n="4"/>ṟitikolagōtrulaina piṁccamu Anni seṭṭini
<lb n="5"/>sōtamaseṭṭini tama taṁḍrināgiseṭṭikini ta
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ma talli prōlāsāniki dharmmuvugānu guḍrivāḍa
<lb n="7"/>kuṁdēśvara śrīmahādēvarakuṁ beṭṭina Akhaṁ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍadīpamu 1 dīniki modavulu 30 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vrīhikṣētra
<lb n="9" break="no"/>mu Ūri Uttaramuna veḍlabōyiniguṁṭa paḍmaṭa
<lb n="10"/>kha 3 grihakṣētramu Ūridakṣīṇamuna veḍlapu 12 ni 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḍuvu 25 mūḍlu vīniṁ jēkoni Eṟṟaṁgommanabōyi
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ni koḍku Annaṁgommanabōyuṁḍu naṁdimānika nitya māneṁ
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ḍu neyi Ācaṁdrārkkamu naḍapi sukha manubhaviṁpaṁgala
<lb n="14" break="no"/>vāru śrī <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> ¤
